## M22: unsafe builtins are allowed inside a `raw` block.
##
## Per GPT-5.5 entry 35: the same `inRawContext()` predicate
## that gates `%x` raw access also gates unsafe builtins.
## The block IS the audit boundary.

sub main()
  x = 42
  raw
    y = @ptrCast(x)          # OK: inside `raw` block
    print(y)
